{"product_id":"volumizing-solid-conditioner-with-linden-flower-extract","title":"Magrada Volumizing Solid Conditioner With Linden Flower Extract 50g","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eGentle on your hair and on the environment. The solid conditioner is eco-friendly and practical to take with you in your suitcase or workout bag.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe combination of the best natural ingredients restores and nourishes hair without making it heavy. Plant-based ingredients, such as linden flowers, cocoa butter, shea butter, and sweet almond oil, leave the hair soft and pliable with a hint of a sweet linden flower aroma reminding you of a warm midsummer night.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eNordic linden flower extract \u003c\/span\u003ehas a moisturising and softening effect suitable for a sensitive or irritated scalp.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eShea butter\u003c\/span\u003e is extracted from the nuts of the shea tree, which is native to Africa. Shea butter softens and moisturises the skin and helps to maintain its moisture balance.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eCocoa butter\u003c\/span\u003e contains plenty of essential fatty acids, which help to improve the protective function of the skin.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003ePro-vitamin B5 \u003c\/span\u003eadds healthy elasticity and shine to your tresses and improves the structure of processed hair.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eAfter washing your hair with a shampoo, massage the conditioner gently into wet ends and then rinse.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Cetearyl Alcohol, Theobroma Cacao (Cocoa) Seed Butter, Behentrimonium Methosulfate, Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter, Prunus Amygdalus Dulcis (Sweet Almond) Oil, Parfum, Tilia Cordata (Linden) Flower Extract, Hexyl Cinnamal, Geraniol\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIngredients of natural origin: 99%.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe list of ingredients may be changed. Please see the packaging for the updated and most accurate list of ingredients.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eparaben-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e SLS-free | alcohol-free\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e silicone-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e vegan\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e cruelty-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e hand-made \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e with a minimal list of ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Magrada Organic Cosmetics","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":48927701696839,"sku":"","price":13.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/magrada-volumizing-solid-conditioner-with-linden-flower-extract-50g-360749.png?v=1739897404","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/volumizing-solid-conditioner-with-linden-flower-extract","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}